{{doc/start}}
Renders recipe cards for all recipes that can be crafted in a specific building. Each card shows inputs, outputs, base craft time, and per-building throughput rates. Backed by [[Module:RecipeCard]]'s <code>building</code> function.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{RecipeCard Building|_base_assembler_i}}
{{RecipeCard Building|id=_base_assembler_i}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
{| class="wikitable"
! Parameter !! Description !! Type !! Status
|-
| <code>1</code> / <code>id</code> || Building template identifier (e.g. <code>_base_assembler_i</code> for Assembler I). || String || Required
|}

== Notes ==
* Recipes are looked up via [[Module:Data/BuildingRecipeIndex]], keyed by building identifier.
* Per-building throughput rates come from [[Module:Data/RecipeCraftingData]].
* If the building has no associated recipes, the template outputs nothing.
* For displaying recipes by item rather than by building, use [[Template:RecipeCard]].
{{doc/end}}
